    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_1_757-844",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "757-844",
      "markText": "在政治体或社会体内，当权得势的阶层，长期封闭在自己的意识形态和思考习惯中，不容易理解这一共同体的其他部分或是基层“细胞”成长的需求，则共同体就可能逐渐趋于僵化，最后趋于澌灭。",
      "totalCount": 882,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=844",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=757&rangeEnd=844"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_3_4194-4267",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4194-4267",
      "markText": "“五胡乱华”的几百年，也正是世界气候史上中古的大寒冷时期，在欧洲历史上引发了所谓“蛮族大入侵”，而中国历史上的五胡乱华，其实都和全球气候改变有关。",
      "totalCount": 697,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4194&rangeEnd=4267",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4194&rangeEnd=4267"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_2_2748-2778",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2748-2778",
      "markText": "一个朝代的盛衰，归结为一句话，就是公权力的核心是不是开放的。",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2748&rangeEnd=2778",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2748&rangeEnd=2778"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_2_1484-1503",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1484-1503",
      "markText": "上面向下选拔人才，一定是挑最听话的人。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1484&rangeEnd=1503",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1484&rangeEnd=1503"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_2_1081-1172",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1081-1172",
      "markText": "朝代刚起来的时候，似乎满地都是人才；朝代结束的时候，人才都不见了。这并不是说天地生才在不同的时段有不同的分布，而是有才之士能不能被吸收到国家的管理机构之中，以维持一个有效的管理体系。",
      "totalCount": 588,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1081&rangeEnd=1172",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1081&rangeEnd=1172"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_1_657-714",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "657-714",
      "markText": "老一代如果活得太长，把持权力太久，就会使得中枢系统的功能衰退。因为老一代的体能已经衰弱，不能再像当年那样应对挑战。",
      "totalCount": 576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=657&rangeEnd=714",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=657&rangeEnd=714"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_4_1510-1571",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1510-1571",
      "markText": "过去的历史教科书上总是说胡人进入中原就被汉化了，其实不然，整个中原也是在不断地接纳胡人文化，逐渐改变、丰富汉人的文化性质。",
      "totalCount": 525,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1510&rangeEnd=1571",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1510&rangeEnd=1571"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_2_2421-2521",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2421-2521",
      "markText": "如果中央的权力团体和社会力量之间没有足够的沟通，公权力的行使往往就不是以维持一个政治共同体的正常运作为目的，而是以公权力压制社会；社会力不能影响政治力的时候，社会力必定像决堤一样，冲破约束，颠覆政权。",
      "totalCount": 496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2421&rangeEnd=2521",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2421&rangeEnd=2521"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_1_364-433",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "364-433",
      "markText": "人体之内，不同器官的功能需要相互配合，任何器官不能过强，也不能过弱。器官的功能不平衡，人就会有疾病，甚至于因为器官丧失功能而造成衰退和死亡",
      "totalCount": 465,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=364&rangeEnd=433",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=364&rangeEnd=433"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_2_1566-1636",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1566-1636",
      "markText": "一个掌握绝对权力的小圈子，如果两三代以后，只是同样形态人物的复制，而两三代之后随着内外环境的改变，必定出现新的挑战，这些领导者就不能应付了。",
      "totalCount": 448,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1566&rangeEnd=1636",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1566&rangeEnd=1636"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_2_923-958",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "923-958",
      "markText": "分久必合、合久必分，都取决于中央政府能不能有效地掌握各主要地区的资源。",
      "totalCount": 442,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=923&rangeEnd=958",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=923&rangeEnd=958"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_21_1852-1921",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "1852-1921",
      "markText": "为什么许多帝国、国家到了后来衰弱了？说到底，第一点是权力会腐蚀人，掌权久了，不舍得放下；第二，他会期望把自己的权力交给子孙，永远把握权力。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=1852&rangeEnd=1921",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=1852&rangeEnd=1921"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_1_1520-1580",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1520-1580",
      "markText": "学历史的人，摊开史料，眼看着人类走过的途径，其间有多少次的衰亡？多少次的覆灭？但是人类从来无法从前面的失败中，吸取经验。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1520&rangeEnd=1580",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1520&rangeEnd=1580"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_23_1990-2089",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "1990-2089",
      "markText": "其实在“自由主义”四个字的后面，真正的潜台词是“我发财是我的命，你饿死是你的命”。如果这一种价值观念不加以改变，如果再没有新的人道精神或是仁者的胸怀，世界将要回到一个现代科技的丛林，人吃人而不见血。",
      "totalCount": 377,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1990&rangeEnd=2089",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1990&rangeEnd=2089"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_9_2668-2765",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2668-2765",
      "markText": "这两大帝国，没有机会保持自己完整的国家，一垮之后分崩离析。相对言之，中国倒是败而未散，超过一个半世纪，中国屡遭挫败却并不放弃努力，蹒跚其行，不断挣扎，居然还保持了领土的完整。这也是历史上的异数。",
      "totalCount": 375,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2668&rangeEnd=2765",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2668&rangeEnd=2765"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_2_3093-3143",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "3093-3143",
      "markText": "如果一个政府的核心团体足够开放，可以不断吸收新鲜血液，不断地面对新问题，这样的核心就不会和百姓脱节。",
      "totalCount": 348,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=673134&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3093&rangeEnd=3143",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6cc32f105a456e6cc42b539?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3093&rangeEnd=3143"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "673134_3_2008-2092",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2008-2092",
